icial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/PCDM/111%2c%e9%87%91%e8%a8%b4%2c252%2c20220418%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"PCDM,111,金訴,252,20220418,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"金訴","JNO":"252","JDATE":"20220418","JTITLE":"洗錢防制法等"}